    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a 'time capsule' find for any serious collector or enthusiast. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original showroom depth and shine, while the interior remains in pristine, factory-new condition with no signs of wear. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership.",
