      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily practicality. The exterior finish retains a brilliant luster, though a keen eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front fascia\u2014honest evidence of its life on the road. There are no major dents or deep scratches to speak of. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are soft and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster consistent with careful use. Every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the power sunroof, dual-zone climate control, and the high-fidelity sound system. Mechanically, this car is exceptionally sound. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, and I have a complete folder of maintenance records available for your review. Most recently, we\u2019ve performed a full synthetic oil",
